title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 4 Evening' game
title_page: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 4 Evening' game
maintext:
DES MOINES, Iowa (AP) _ The winning numbers in Sunday evening’s drawing of the Iowa Lottery’s “Pick 4 Evening” game were:
9-4-5-6
(nine, four, five, six)
